Created from

https://developers.google.com/static/kml/documentation/KML_Samples.kml

I've really only tested the results on Google Maps and Google Earth.
Other software seems to accept results well enough such as GPS
Visualizer, but I haven't tested it beyond converting the results
to a .gpx file.

For now, this is the best way to visualize multiple route runs.

Note the colors file which contains information specifying how
different colors can be displayed.
